# Hooks run under bash (WSL) and tests byte-diff PowerShell output (LF, \r
# stripped) against golden/fixture files. Windows runners default to
# autocrlf=true, which would rewrite these to CRLF on checkout and break the
# diffs — pin every text file to LF on all platforms.
* text=auto eol=lf

*.png binary
*.wav binary
*.mp4 binary
*.ico binary
